objectives: 1   Objectives of zone•  To enable a mix of business and warehouse uses, and specialised retail premises that require a large floor area, in locations that are close to, and that support the viability of, centres.•  To cater specifically for uses that require a high degree of visibility and accessibility to passing traffic and that generate a high proportion of single purpose vehicle trips.•  To enable the establishment of a business, technology, bulky goods and light industrial precinct at Surf Beach.•  To encourage site amalgamation and creation of a highway service precinct on land at Batemans Bay.•  To support the nearby local business centre of Moruya without adversely impacting on the viability of that centre.
